graph TD
    User[User Browser] --> CF[CloudFront CDN]
    CF --> S3[S3 Static Hosting]
    S3 --> App[React App - Vite/TypeScript]

    App --> APIGW[API Gateway - REST]
    APIGW --> CogAuth{Cognito Authorizer}

    CogAuth -->|Auth Routes - No Auth| Lambda[Lambda Function - Express]
    CogAuth -->|Protected Routes - JWT| Lambda

    Lambda --> DDB[(DynamoDB - 9 Tables)]
    Lambda --> Cognito[Cognito User Pool]
    Lambda --> SES[AWS SES]
    Lambda --> SSM[SSM Parameter Store]
    Lambda --> IoT[IoT Core]
    Lambda --> StripeAPI[Stripe API]

    App --> StaticJSON[Static Config - 7 JSON Files]
    IoT --> |MQTT WebSocket| App

    subgraph "Frontend - totem-app"
        App
        StaticJSON
    end

    subgraph "AWS Backend - totem-api"
        APIGW
        CogAuth
        Lambda
        DDB
        Cognito
        SES
        SSM
        IoT
    end

    subgraph "External Services"
        StripeAPI
        CF
    end

    classDef aws fill:#FF9900,stroke:#232F3E,color:white
    classDef app fill:#36B37E,stroke:#006644,color:white
    classDef ext fill:#6772E5,stroke:#32325D,color:white

    class APIGW,CogAuth,Lambda,DDB,Cognito,SES,SSM,IoT aws
    class User,App,StaticJSON app
    class StripeAPI,CF,S3 ext
